Patch 0073 — closes the three remaining items from the institutional review.

(1) CHOKEPOINT INDEX (lib/news/chokepoint-index.ts)
    Dedicated 1-5 severity scale per canonical chokepoint category,
    separate from the binary STRATEGIC_CHOKEPOINT flag. 17 categories:
      Severity 5  EUV Litho (ASML), HALEU (LEU), Naval Reactor (BWXT)
      Severity 4  CoWoS (TSM), HBM (SKH/Samsung/Micron), AI GPU (NVDA),
                  Aero Engines (GE/RR/RTX)
      Severity 3  Transformers, Switchgear HV, Gas Turbines Large,
                  Liquid Cooling AI, Optical Interconnect 800G+,
                  Grid Interconnect, Missile RF Seekers,
                  Rare Earth Magnets, Western Uranium, ABF Substrates
    Detected by text pattern OR by primary-ticker match. Returns
    {severity, label, competitors, rationale, beneficiary tickers}.

(2) MACRO INSIGHT BANNER (auto-derived)
    Top of /strategic-visibility now shows a 1-line headline + sub-line
    derived from the by-theme + by-flag + by-chokepoint distribution.
    Three primary patterns it detects:
      "Markets are repricing scarce industrial capacity — not software"
        (when ≥80% of contracts are AI infra / energy / defence / semi)
      "AI infrastructure capex dominating"
        (when AI infra > energy+defence)
      "Energy + defence sovereignty is the dominant capital cycle"
        (when energy+defence > AI infra)
    Sub-line shows counts + cumulative book value + chokepoint-of-3.

(3) WORKING CAPITAL INTENSITY — numeric (0-100)
    Replaces the string "Low / Medium / High" with a sortable/filterable
    integer score. Naval shipbuilding 90, fab 60, mid-margin defence 50,
    annuity infra 15, AI take-or-pay 5. Coloured badge (green→amber→red).

Wiring: classifyChokepoint + workingCapitalIntensityNumeric called
inside the SV qualification block; emitted on items.push; persisted to
ledger; backfilled into seed entries via enrichSeedEntry.

Cache key bumped v25 → v26. tsc clean.
